txt.en: Isengard's forces have begun letting down their guard in the shadow of Núrzum's presence. Guarded by the ice left in his wake, the Orcs have built fires and tents.
Isengard's forces have begun letting down their guard in the shadow of Núrzum's presence. Guarded by the ice left in his wake, the Orcs have built fires and tents.
Orc-tents and bonfires can be found at the ice-spire left in Núrzum's wake.\n\nYou should tear down the tents and bonfires of the Orcs.
You have torn down the comforts of the unguarded Orcs settling in Núrzum's shadow.\n\nNo Orcs will settle openly in Wildermore while its people still inhabit these lands.
